Comment: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,========= Dialogue =========
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{You forgot something.}Ông để quên nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:13.41,Main,split,0,0,0,,{A-As you can see, I'm just some old man.}Như anh thấy đó, tôi chỉ là một lão già.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.28,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Unfortunately, I don't have\Nany children, either...}Tôi e là tôi cũng không có con...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{I never said it was yours.}Tôi đâu có nói là của ông.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:20.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, was it a customer's?\NI will hold it, then...}Ồ, của khách hàng à? Vậy tôi sẽ giữ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.09,Main,split,0,0,0,,{How about it?}Thế thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:26.62,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Wanna go somewhere?}Muốn đi đâu đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:29.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's a little to early to go to bed...}Giờ mà đi ngủ thì hơi sớm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:31.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm an early riser... I sleep too early.}Tôi là người dậy sớm, ngủ sớm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:35.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{If you want a prim and proper life,\NI have just the place for you. [9 frames]}Nếu muốn một cuộc sống kỷ luật như vậy,\Ntôi có chỗ hợp với ông.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{A hotel where you get three meals\Nand a bodyguard, all for free.}Một khách sạn với ba bữa ăn mỗi ngày,\Ncó vệ sĩ, tất cả đều miễn phí.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:40.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure that's impossible\Nwithout a reservation.}Chắc chắn họ yêu cầu phải đặt phòng trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:43.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm talking about Hotel Prison,\NTeddy Bomber.}Khách sạn Nhà Tù đó, Bom Gấu Bông.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'd rather not, Spike Spiegel.}Chắc tao không nhận đâu, Spike Spiegel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, you know me?}Ông biết tôi là ai ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's a popular story among criminals}Tội phạm bị truy nã\Ncó nói với nhau một câu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:56.53,Main,split,0,0,0,,{that we never want to be\Ncaught by you, or by Andy.}Đừng để bị Spike hay Andy bắt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:57.24,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Andy?}Andy ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{I will fulfill my objective!}Tao sẽ hoàn thành mục tiêu của mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{It won't blow up.}Nó không nổ đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{I took out the ignition pin.}Tôi rút chốt đánh lửa ra rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{3 million woolongs,\Ngraciously accepted.}Tôi sẽ lấy ba triệu woolong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{That's not the only bear.}Vẫn còn các con gấu khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{You'll die, too.}Ông cũng sẽ chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{I love them to death.}Tao thích các vụ nổ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{Why do you want to blow\Nstuff up so much?}Sao ông lại thích cho nổ tung mọi thứ thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ya wanna know? I am giving a warning.}Muốn biết ư? Tao đang đưa ra lời cảnh báo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:51.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{I am ringing a bell of warning!}Tao gióng một hồi chuông báo động.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{All right, be mindful of what I say!}Nghe đây. Nghe cho kỹ lời tao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{Andy!}Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:13.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{Andy? [9 frames]}Andy ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{Call me Wyatt Earp.}Gọi ta là Wyatt Earp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{You! Teddy Bomber, serial bomber!}Ngươi! Kẻ đánh bom liên hoàn,\NBom Gấu Bông!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:24.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Me?!}Ta ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{The fact that you'd plant\Na bomb here today was easy}Sau khi phân tích\Nkhuôn mẫu hành vi phạm tội của ngươi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:32.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{for me to figure out after\Ncalculating your criminal cycles.}chẳng khó gì cho ta\Nđể tìm ra ngươi sẽ đặt bom ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{You don't think that's him?}Ngươi không nghĩ là ông ấy ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.88,Main,split,0,0,0,,{He's a security guard!}Ông ấy là bảo vệ!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.25,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Just look at his face!}Nhìn ông ấy cho kỹ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{In this day and age, a face means nothing.}Thời đại ngày nay,\Nkhông nhìn mặt mà phán được.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{Then what is the basis of your theory?!}Ngươi dựa vào cái quái gì mà nói thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{That is...}Ừ thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:49.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{my gut instinct. Yes, inspiration!}Trực giác của ta.\NHay ta nên nói, nguồn cảm hứng!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:52.77,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Hey, wait!}Này, đợi đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:53.86,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Wait!}Chờ đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh shit!}Ôi, chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:12.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{That's why I said Teddy Bomber\Nwas that guy, you idiot!}Đó là lý do\Nta nói gã đó là Bom Gấu Bông đó, đồ ngốc!
