Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:32.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{Nope. Young Men's Cowboy Association!}Không. Hiệp Hội Cao Bồi Trẻ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh? Such a thing exists?}Chưa từng nghe đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{But, he got kicked out soon after joining.}Sau khi gia nhập không lâu thì gã bị đuổi.
