Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:40.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{Well, he's coming.}Ừ, hắn đang đến đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
