Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{This lead the way to its papa.}Chú cún này giúp chúng tôi tìm bố gấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{I think I woulda known in either case.}Tôi cũng biết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:00.02,Main,split,0,0,0,,{You guys just don't quit, do you?}Các ngươi không từ bỏ đúng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:01.01,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Speak for yourself.}Xem ai nói câu đó kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Why do you want to blow\Nthings up so much?}Sao ông cứ thích cho nổ tung mọi thứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:04.92,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Ya wanna know?}Muốn biết ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.53,Main,split,0,0,0,,{I am giving out a warning.}Tao đang đưa ra lời cảnh báo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:10.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{Listen, in this world, the root of all evil...}Nghe này, trong thế giới này,\Ngốc rễ của mọi tội lỗi là...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:24.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{A horse...}Một con ngựa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{A cowboy...}Một tên cao bồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.21,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Hey, you! Teddy Bomber!}Này, tên kia! Bom Gấu Bông!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.53,Main,split,0,0,0,,{M-Me?!}Ai? Tôi ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.07,Main,split,0,0,0,,{See, I told you.}Thấy chưa, tôi nói rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.64,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Or is it you over there?}Hay là cái tên kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{Do you have no memory?}Ngươi không nhớ gì hết ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{We met just yesterday!}Chúng ta vừa mới gặp hôm qua!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hm? I have no recollection.}Ta không nhớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:45.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{You!}Đồ khốn...
