Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:46.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! If they think they can get away\Nwith this, they are sorely mistaken...}Lũ khốn kiếp! Nếu nghĩ sẽ thoát khỏi vụ này,\Nthì chúng lầm to rồi!
