Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:36.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{Now that I have both of\Nyou here, I will tell you.}Giờ cả hai đều ở đây,\Ntao có điều muốn nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:39.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{The reason why I continue to\Nblow buildings up. That is because—}Tao tiếp tục cho nổ tung các tòa nhà vì...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{Today, we are going to settle\Nthe score once and for all.}Hôm nay, ta giải quyết cho xong vụ này.
