Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.45,Main,split,0,0,0,,{What?! Get outta the way, dammit!}Gì cơ? Tránh ra! Chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{Farewell... [9 frames]}Rảnh nợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it,\Nthey were brave young men...}Nghĩ lại thì,\Ntụi nó cũng là bọn trai trẻ dũng cảm.
