Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:34.36,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Yeah, yeah.}Ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:37.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{But anyway...}{\i1}Mà này,{\i0}
